<Author>EbenezerS
<Content>Great Value - Great Service This was my first experience of Candlewood Suites and I pleased to have stayed here.It was recommended to me by the company which I was contracting for so I wasn't expecting it to be too great.However, the room was clean and comfortable, there was free high speed internet and the small kitchen area was more than sufficient for my needs.Service from the front desk was excellent and nothing was too much trouble - any problems being sorted immediately.I will most definitely stay here again when I'm in Phoenix - unless the company pays for a five star resort!! 
